MSSM, Feynman gauge
 Constraints 
 Name |> Expression                                                                                                      <|> Comment                      <|
pi    |4*atan(1)                                                                                                          |
CW    |sqrt(1-SW^2)                                                                                                       |cos of the Weinberg angle
S2W   |2*SW*CW                                                                                                            |
C2W   |CW^2-SW^2                                                                                                          |
MW    |MZ*CW                                                                                                              |W mass
c12   |sqrt(1-s12^2)                                                                                                      |parameter  of C-K-M matrix
c23   |sqrt(1-s23^2)                                                                                                      |parameter  of C-K-M matrix
c13   |sqrt(1-s13^2)                                                                                                      |parameter  of C-K-M matrix
Vud   |c12                                                                                                                |C-K-M matrix element
Vus   |s12                                                                                                                |C-K-M matrix element
Vcs   |Vud                                                                                                                |C-K-M matrix element
Vcd   |-Vus                                                                                                               |C-K-M matrix element
sb    |tb/sqrt(1+tb^2)                                                                                                    |Sinus beta
cb    |sqrt(1-sb^2)                                                                                                       |Cosine beta
t2b   |2*tb/(1-tb^2)                                                                                                      |
c2b   |cb^2-sb^2                                                                                                          |cos(2b)
s2b   |4*sb*cb/2                                                                                                          |sin(2b)
ls3   |Ml*Al/Sqrt2*EE/SW/MW/cb                                                                                            |Tau soft coupling (Rosiek notation)
MSne  |sqrt(c2b*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml2^2)/CW                                                                                     |e-sneutrino mass
MSnm  |sqrt(c2b*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml2^2)/CW                                                                                     |mu-sneutrino mass
MSnl  |sqrt(c2b*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml3^2)/CW                                                                                     |tau-sneutrino mass
MSeL  |sqrt(-c2b*(CW^2-SW^2)*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml2^2)/CW                                                                        |left selectron mass
MSeR  |sqrt(-SW^2*c2b*MW^2+CW^2*Mr2^2)/CW                                                                                 |right selectron mass
MSmL  |sqrt(-c2b*(CW^2-SW^2)*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml2^2)/CW                                                                        |left smuon mass
MSmR  |sqrt(-SW^2*c2b*MW^2+CW^2*Mr2^2)/CW                                                                                 |right smuon mass
MSlLL |Ml3^2+Ml^2-MW^2/CW^2*(1/2-SW^2)*c2b                                                                                |
MSlLR |MW*SW*Sqrt2*cb*ls3/EE-Ml*mu*tb                                                                                     |
MSlRR |Mr3^2+Ml^2-MW^2/CW^2*SW^2*c2b                                                                                      |
