MSl2  |sqrt((MSlLL+MSlRR+sqrt((MSlLL-MSlRR)^2+4*MSlLR^2))/2)                                                              |heavy stau mass
MSlth |atan2(-2*MSlLR, -MSlLL+MSlRR)/2                                                                                    |stau mixing angle
