Zuas4 |1092363/10000000                                                                                                   |
Zur0  |1+4*Zuas4/3/pi+(1611/100-104/100*(5-663/Mt/100))*(Zuas4/pi)^2                                                      |
ZuQMt |if(sqrt(Mq3*Mu3)-MZ, sqrt(Mq3*Mu3), MZ)                                                                            |
